alert.note: Alert for Del Norte Interior; Northern Humboldt Interior (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: Flood Watch issued September 25 at 12:31PM PDT until September 26 at 11:00AM PDT by NWS Eureka
info.description: ...FLOOD WATCH REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 11 PM PDT THIS EVENING... * WHAT...Flooding caused by excessive rainfall continues to be possible. * WHERE...A portion of northwest California, including the following areas, Coastal Del Norte, Del Norte Interior and Northern Humboldt Interior. * WHEN...Until 11 PM PDT this evening. * IMPACTS...Flooding may occur in poor drainage and urban areas. Storm drains and ditches may become clogged with debris. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS... - http://www.weather.gov/safety/flood
info.instruction: You should monitor later forecasts and be alert for possible Flood Warnings. Those living in areas prone to flooding should be prepared to take action should flooding develop.
